title: Winston Churchill Tribute
itunes:title: Winston Churchill Tribute
description: TODAY ON THE CIGAR AUTHORITY SCOTT KOLESAIRE FROM WINSTON CHURCHILL CIGARS JOINS DAVE GAROFALO , MR JONATHAN AND PRODUCER CHUCK AS WE PAY TRIBUTE TO THE WORLD'S MOST FAMOUS CIGAR SMOKER - WINSTON CHURCHILL! TODAY THE BOYS LIGHT UP THE WINSTON CHURCHILL BLENHEIM "7" X 48", AND THE CAMACHO CANDELLA. SIT BACK, LIGHT UP AND ENJOY THE FINER THINGS IN LIFE WITH THE CIGAR AUTHORITY!
